                <note rend="inline" type="source">798.94/5471: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China (<persName corresp="frus1932v03#p_JNT1" type="to"
                            >Johnson</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-08-06T16:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 6, 1932—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>243. Your 905, August 6, 11 a.m. Have you discussed this with your military staff
                    and with your diplomatic colleagues? What are their opinions?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1932v03#p_CWR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
